dct_title_s: The National Geographic magazine map of Central America, Cuba, Porto Rico, and the islands of the Caribbean Sea
dct_alternative_sm: Map of Central America, Cuba, Porto Rico, and the islands of the Caribbean Sea
dct_description_sm: prepared by the American Bank Note Co. ; Gilbert H. Grosvenor, editor.
Shows railroads, steamship routes, and submarine telegraph lines.
Depths shown by gradient tints, isolines, and spot heights.
"Copyright, 1913, by American Bank Note Company, New York."
Supplement to the February, 1913, issue of the National Geographic magazine.
Includes inset and cross-section of Panama Canal Zone.
